                    <span>I barely received my copy, and the <br>advice/help on being a better writer<br>is pretty good. One thing that stands <br>out in the book is the issue of vulgarity,<br>and that is simply a no when it comes<br>to writing journalism. The other areas<br>are well explained, and i tell any one <br>who is reading this small paragraph, get it,<br>it is worth it! It will definitely help you<br>get more creative with your writing, this is <br>like the bloom's taxonomy of writing.</span>
                  
              
